      "kind": "parameters",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "A rendering context returned by the function ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/AGL-collection",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "ctx"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The drawable object—which must be a Carbon window—to attach to the AGL rendering context. You need to supply a ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "CGrafPtr",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " data type obtained from a valid window. The Window Manager function ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "GetWindowPort",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": "  returns the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "CGrafPtr",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " associated with a Carbon window. To disable rendering for a rendering context, pass ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "NULL",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "draw"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return-value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Returns ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "GL_FALSE",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " if it fails for any reason, ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "GL_TRUE",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " otherwise. If an error occurs, call the function ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglGetError",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to determine what the error is.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After calling this function, AGL directs subsequent OpenGL rendering calls to the specified rendering context to modify the window content. In addition, the function ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "aglSetDrawable",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " performs all of the actions performed by ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglUpdateContext",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When a rendering context is initially attached to the  window, its viewport is set to the full size of the window. If the rendering context is subsequently attached to the same window, its viewport is unaltered.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
